#: ../../library/sunaudio.rst:162
msgid ""
"This is a companion module to :mod:`sunaudiodev` which defines useful "
"symbolic constants like :const:`MIN_GAIN`, :const:`MAX_GAIN`, "
":const:`SPEAKER`, etc. The names of the constants are the same names as used"
" in the C include file ``<sun/audioio.h>``, with the leading string "
"``AUDIO_`` stripped."
